Comment: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ENDING
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold bells and a bird...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose they were symbols of old Jaya?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.89,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno, but I think they were \Npart of some sort of model.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.14,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This here's called a South Bird, \Nand they still exist on this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Do they have weird calls?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Just like the logbook says!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.28,0:02:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sailors have long used South Birds to...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go catch this bird! Right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! What for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.58,0:02:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we need a bird?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.88,0:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely! The Knock-Up Stream \Nyou're heading for tomorrow
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.09,0:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is located directly south of this cape.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.43,0:02:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to get there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.47,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're on the open sea, \Nthere's no way to get your bearings!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.23,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading for ocean, not an island, \Nso we have no guide to rely on!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.85,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll use the bird's behavior for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.32,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the sad tale of your \NMontblanc family at the pub.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It moved me, Cricket.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.78,0:03:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure someone else struggled to \Nget has a special flavor all its own!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna know what people call me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hyena!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come! Dodge!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These praying mantises aren't normal!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.34,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our net!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this forest?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The South Bird is the bugs' control tower!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is a {\i1}bird{\i0} controlling {\i1}bugs{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here! Where's it coming from?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.33,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? I hear something different...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Up ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Boulders?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're rolling this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.34,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it dung beetle dung?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! They're bugs!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladybugs!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're huge! Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn things!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is your mole cricket army attacking me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way! \NDo you think you can beat me?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it, but I can't see it...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Slug!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt! Throw salt!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Your Somersault Kick!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Not that kind of "salt"!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.96,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of running! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Luffy! Bear-bees are really poisonous!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireflies!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.30,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockroaches!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pigs!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We gladly accept fights people pick with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Saruyama Alliance!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.66,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over your gold quietly, \Nor else you're gonna pay dearly!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you figure?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Old man!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey Punch!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it's dangerous for kids \Nto swing stuff like that around!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.62,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess we should \Nget this midnight show started!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.34,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...Snipe!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Bellamy! Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.66,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of our captain's \N"Spring-Spring Fruit" powers?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Speechless, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean up the trash! Take care of 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for your Saruyama Alliance!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.48,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just an old man and \Na couple of overgrown apes!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackpot, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.66,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Would you look at that? \NWonderful gold bullion!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more! Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This's a big haul!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.17,0:08:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys... aren't qualified to have that gold...!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Qualified?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}this{\i0} qualified enough for ya?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Chop!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're way stronger than you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.77,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more qualified do we \Nneed to be to steal treasure?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, old man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, old-timer!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Havoc Sonar!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sarquiss!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} end his life.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.26,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that again... \NThe power of the Spring-Spring Fruit...!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Shojo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...Snipe!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shojo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.38,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-timer! We found gold! A bell-shaped ingot!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.02,0:09:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It matches what's listed in the logbook! \NIt mentions bells!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go. Load the gold on board.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grow up, old man!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.04,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This "city of gold" is just a \Nproduct of Noland's imagination!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.67,0:10:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna be a pirate in the coming new era,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.88,0:10:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,then you need to realize that dreams never come true!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of gold {\i1}does{\i0} exist!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! Don't go wild! It's a small house!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, kiddo...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.95,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A hatchling who doesn't have the \Nguts to pick fights with dreams...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...is in no position to talk about pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.28,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck. We couldn't even see a single one...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.82,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw one, but there was no time \Nfor the bird, with all those bugs...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All we did was run...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.04,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeesh! Seven people, and you get zilch?! \NGet it together, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run any more!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.31,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"You really think you can catch us? Idiots!"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.89,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He came here to tell us that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I'll shoot you good!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All I needed was to see one.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Old guy! We caught a bird!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Old diamond-head!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Masira!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shojo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.50,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Who did this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Gimme a hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.30,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The Going Merry...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.98,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! Who did this?! \NDammit! Who was it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.90,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Old guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, old guy! Are you awake?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we could do! We're pathetic!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.45,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But... there's still time to strengthen the ship before sunup...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, old guy! Tell us what happened first!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.50,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's okay. Don't worry about it. \NDoesn't matter now...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, you need to...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.05,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Great! You caught yourselves a South Bird!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The gold... It's been stolen!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.11,0:13:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's alright... Forget about that junk...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to focus on...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "junk"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.54,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It took you ten long years of diving into the ocean
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and torturing your body \Nuntil you found that gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.42,0:13:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright... This's {\i1}our{\i0} problem...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.89,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If they all work on it, the Saruyama Alliance
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,can fix and reinforce that ship, no problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have 'em finish in time for morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.73,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any trouble \Nwith your departure tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.19,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! \NWe {\i1}will{\i0} send you into the sky, without fail!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-timer...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellamy's mark...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Want help?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can do it alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.05,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Luffy! Don't be stupid! \NWe set sail in only three hours!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.93,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run along the coast, will I reach \Nthe town from this afternoon?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! Where're you going?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.67,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool! \NDo you know who you're dealing—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna stop him, use this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kid...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.80,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm empty now! \NThat's every last drop of water in my body!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I won't sweat a single drop!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This ol' drunk is broke and dry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.31,0:15:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,O, God of Alcohol, thank you for today!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess there's no such thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A newspaper?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see! What bad news is there today?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this isn't a newspaper. \NIt's a stack of wanted posters...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.83,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this is a lawless town! \NI'm sick of meeting new bad guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is that spineless kid from this afternoon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that sky island talk was a real hoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty million, I believe he was worth...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! I had a little too much to drink!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.98,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.82,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 10, 100, 1,000, 10,000, \N100,000, 1,000,000, 10,000,000...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes! I really did drink too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.95,0:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 10, 100, 1,000, 10,000, \N100,000, 1,000,000, 10,000,000...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...100,000,000!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three hours, Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If we delay our departure any more than that...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...you'll lose your chance to go to the sky island!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.32,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've done reckless diving day after day
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.57,0:16:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without letting those bubbles \Ndisappear from his body!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.37,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a duel with the man \Nwho screwed up my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we could do! We're pathetic!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.48,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those big apes were hilarious!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.48,0:17:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They had huge gashes all over and had tears and snot dripping down
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as they cried, "Old-timer!"
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's that important, \Nthey should've protected him better!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about lame!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't help it; they were up against you and Bellamy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.92,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, our captain is a major \Nrookie worth 55 million berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?! It's the middle of the night!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.18,0:17:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This afternoon! Those guys in here, they...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.31,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Bellamy! You're still here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.35,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta get out of here! \NYou're in the most danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.61,0:18:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about? Me, in danger?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,60 million?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.95,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Those two from this afternoon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.21,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bounties are higher than yours, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dead meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.05,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?! Crap! \NWe laughed at the {\i1}wrong{\i0} people!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Think they remember what we look like?! \NIt's dangerous to stay here!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I never met anyone with a 100 million bounty!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.03,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! You fools! \NScared of a few scraps of paper!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.25,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have knotholes for eyes?! \NYou saw their leader!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Made it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that there were once pirates
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.76,0:19:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who faked their own wanted posters \Nto make names for themselves?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.22,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,People'd see their bounties \Nand just curl up and surrender,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even though they could've won in a fight...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you guys now!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.19,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw how weak they are, \Nbut look at you now! You're pathetic!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.75,0:20:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! \NBoy, those bastards had me scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellamy's right... someone \Nwith a bounty of 100 million
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.37,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,has {\i1}gotta{\i0} be involved with some pretty bad stuff,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.17,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but then why hasn't he been in the papers?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.76,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely! I ain't heard of any straw hat kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.48,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! Had me scared for a minute there!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.18,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Back to drinking! Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellamy! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To think he'd call me out...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.84,0:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.22,0:21:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard the rumors about you...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You got business with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.60,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Give back old diamond-head's gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.58,0:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were goin' to a sky island. \NHow'd it go?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.00,0:23:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to head into the sky... \Nafter I beat you up!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.63,0:23:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All you ever say is dream-like crap...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.84,0:23:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, I can make you \Ndream forever... in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.88,0:23:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So long, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.84,0:23:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.34,0:23:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,100 Million Man! \NWorld's Greatest Power and Pirate Blackbeard!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.56,0:23:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
